CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 5, 1975, page 14, reads: "Mr. and Mrs. William Lewis.....admiring their gifts."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. William Lewis, wearing fur stole, and Mr. William Lewis, wearing light colored suit with dark lapels and bow tie, holding wrapped gift, at their 42nd wedding anniversary party at Lemont on Mt. Washington
